293
00:15:20,429 --> 00:15:23,396
[music playing]

294
00:16:06,896 --> 00:16:09,129
-Did you sleep OK, Yui?

295
00:16:09,163 --> 00:16:10,463
-Yeah.

296
00:16:10,496 --> 00:16:12,563
Can you help me, Shota?

297
00:16:12,596 --> 00:16:14,329
I want to go outside.

298
00:16:14,363 --> 00:16:15,463
-I'm sorry.

299
00:16:15,496 --> 00:16:19,163
I wanna let you out,
but I'm afraid I can't.

300
00:16:19,196 --> 00:16:23,429
-I wanna go out there
and find mommy and daddy.

301
00:16:23,463 --> 00:16:26,496
I wanna find them too, but
there's no way you can--

302
00:16:26,529 --> 00:16:27,929
-Don't be so upset.

303
00:16:27,963 --> 00:16:29,829
It's all right.

304
00:16:29,863 --> 00:16:31,129
I know a secret.

305
00:16:31,163 --> 00:16:33,063
I can get out of this
barrier with your help.

306
00:16:33,096 --> 00:16:34,363
-Huh?

307
00:16:34,396 --> 00:16:38,196
-All you have to do
is stand up, Shota.

308
00:16:38,229 --> 00:16:40,063
Hold up your hand.

309
00:16:40,096 --> 00:16:42,163
Like this.

310
00:16:42,196 --> 00:16:42,663
-Really?

311
00:16:53,563 --> 00:16:56,563
How did we do that?

312
00:16:56,596 --> 00:16:58,596
-It's a secret.

313
00:16:58,629 --> 00:17:01,629
Let's go.

314
00:17:01,663 --> 00:17:04,096
-Well, Hiyosu, have you
figured anything out?

315
00:17:04,129 --> 00:17:04,663
-Yes.

316
00:17:04,696 --> 00:17:05,896
A few things.

317
00:17:05,929 --> 00:17:07,329
Check out these figured.

318
00:17:07,363 --> 00:17:07,829
-Huh?

319
00:17:07,863 --> 00:17:10,763
Oh, I see.

320
00:17:10,796 --> 00:17:12,629
-Just as we suspected, right?

321
00:17:18,729 --> 00:17:19,663
-Yui.

322
00:17:19,696 --> 00:17:20,229
Shota.

323
00:17:20,263 --> 00:17:21,763
Where are they?

324
00:17:21,796 --> 00:17:23,163
No, they couldn't have.

325
00:17:23,196 --> 00:17:24,463
-Rangiku, what's wrong?

326
00:17:24,496 --> 00:17:26,196
-Captain, the
barrier's been broken.

327
00:17:26,229 --> 00:17:28,396
-What the hell?

328
00:17:28,429 --> 00:17:31,129
There are still traces of
their spiritual pressure.

329
00:17:31,163 --> 00:17:33,696
How did they break that barrier?

330
00:17:33,729 --> 00:17:35,729
-I can't imagine
how they did this.

331
00:17:35,763 --> 00:17:36,863
-It's hard to tell.

332
00:17:36,896 --> 00:17:38,696
-We have to start
looking for them.

333
00:17:38,729 --> 00:17:39,463
-Yes, you're right.

334
00:17:39,496 --> 00:17:40,796
I agree.

335
00:17:40,829 --> 00:17:42,096
-Captain Ukitake.

336
00:17:42,129 --> 00:17:45,796
-We have the results of
the analysis you requested.

337
00:17:45,829 --> 00:17:48,663
-Rangiku, you go out there
and start looking for then.

338
00:17:48,696 --> 00:17:50,763
I'll come join you as
soon as I finish up here.

339
00:17:50,796 --> 00:17:51,429
-Right.

340
00:17:51,463 --> 00:17:52,696
Understood, Captain.

341
00:17:52,729 --> 00:17:54,363
So, what do you have for us?

342
00:17:54,396 --> 00:17:55,829
-I'll begin with the conclusion.

343
00:17:55,863 --> 00:17:58,329
Yui Toyokawa is a clone.

344
00:17:58,363 --> 00:18:01,063
It appears she was created
by the mock Arrancar.

345
00:18:01,096 --> 00:18:03,029
-Are you sure about that?

346
00:18:03,063 --> 00:18:04,329
-Absolutely.

347
00:18:04,363 --> 00:18:06,763
She was a human being with
strong latent spirit energy

348
00:18:06,796 --> 00:18:09,429
before she was killed.

349
00:18:09,463 --> 00:18:11,363
That's probably why
the mock Arrancar

350
00:18:11,396 --> 00:18:14,863
was attracted to her
in the first place.

351
00:18:14,896 --> 00:18:17,463
Unfortunately for us,
absorbing her soul

352
00:18:17,496 --> 00:18:20,163
boosted its powers by
an incredible amount.

353
00:18:20,196 --> 00:18:22,063
Exactly how much,
we can't tell yet.

354
00:18:22,096 --> 00:18:24,729
At the very least,
it gave the Arrancar

355
00:18:24,763 --> 00:18:26,396
the ability to
create attack clones

356
00:18:26,429 --> 00:18:28,863
while the real
form, the main body,

357
00:18:28,896 --> 00:18:30,563
remains hidden and
gains strength.

358
00:18:30,596 --> 00:18:33,029
This explains a lot about
the pace of the Arrancar

359
00:18:33,063 --> 00:18:34,563
attacks the level
of their success.

360
00:18:34,596 --> 00:18:38,063
It absorbed a huge number
of souls of a short time.

361
00:18:38,096 --> 00:18:39,896
I'm afraid that's
all we have for now.

362
00:18:39,929 --> 00:18:41,163
-I see.

363
00:18:41,196 --> 00:18:43,129
However, it seemed
to me that girl

364
00:18:43,163 --> 00:18:46,396
was very much i
control of herself.

365
00:18:46,429 --> 00:18:48,296
AKON: It's likely that
it was all an act.

366
00:18:48,329 --> 00:18:50,796
She's definitely being
controlled by the enemy.

367
00:18:50,829 --> 00:18:52,096
-What's the matter?

368
00:18:52,129 --> 00:18:54,263
HITSUGAYA: If that's true,
and we kill the originating

369
00:18:54,296 --> 00:18:55,463
Arrancar--

370
00:18:55,496 --> 00:18:58,896
AKON: That child's soul
will be destroyed as well.

371
00:18:58,929 --> 00:19:01,863
-Uh-- OkK.

372
00:19:01,896 --> 00:19:02,996
-Wait a minute.

373
00:19:03,029 --> 00:19:05,663
If Yui Toyokawa has such
strong spiritual power,

374
00:19:05,696 --> 00:19:07,796
then why wouldn't her
brother have it is well?

375
00:19:07,829 --> 00:19:09,596
-That's very insightful.

376
00:19:09,629 --> 00:19:11,663
Since they're related,
there's a good possibility

377
00:19:11,696 --> 00:19:13,529
that his level is
the same as hers.

378
00:19:13,563 --> 00:19:14,863
-That's it.

379
00:19:14,896 --> 00:19:17,496
She wasn't able to do it alone,
so she used Shota's power

380
00:19:17,529 --> 00:19:19,096
to break the Kido barrier.

381
00:19:19,129 --> 00:19:24,263
The enemy lured him out
there to absorb his soul!

382
00:19:24,296 --> 00:19:25,463
RANGIKU (VOICEOVER): Shota.

383
00:19:25,496 --> 00:19:26,196
Where did you go?

384
00:19:30,663 --> 00:19:33,363
There you are.

385
00:19:33,396 --> 00:19:33,863
Shota.

386
00:19:33,896 --> 00:19:35,329
Yui!

387
00:19:35,363 --> 00:19:36,829
-Yes, Rangiku?

388
00:19:36,863 --> 00:19:38,696
-How did you get
through that barrier?

389
00:19:38,729 --> 00:19:39,496
-Ha!

390
00:19:39,529 --> 00:19:41,063
It was easy as pie.

391
00:19:41,096 --> 00:19:42,663
We didn't even break a sweat.

392
00:19:42,696 --> 00:19:43,396
-You're in danger.

393
00:19:43,429 --> 00:19:45,463
Come back with me now.

394
00:19:45,496 --> 00:19:47,629
-Don't get in my way.

395
00:19:47,663 --> 00:19:48,129
-Yui?

396
00:19:51,663 --> 00:19:52,463
-What's going on?

397
00:19:59,529 --> 00:20:00,463
-Yui--

398
00:20:00,496 --> 00:20:01,463
-Her spiritual
power is tremendous.

399
00:20:18,263 --> 00:20:19,696
[laughter]

400
00:20:25,596 --> 00:20:28,063
-The attack's started.

401
00:20:28,096 --> 00:20:29,196
-Well, well.

402
00:20:29,229 --> 00:20:31,496
It must feel it's strong
enough to make its move.

403
00:20:41,263 --> 00:20:43,163
-Please, Shota.

404
00:20:43,196 --> 00:20:45,596
I want you to come over here.

405
00:20:45,629 --> 00:20:46,563
-What's going on?

406
00:20:46,596 --> 00:20:47,296
Don't move.

407
00:20:47,329 --> 00:20:49,029
