00:21:29,329 --> 00:21:30,763
-Yui!

419
00:21:30,796 --> 00:21:32,263
-Shota.

420
00:21:32,296 --> 00:21:34,263
-What are you doing?

421
00:21:34,296 --> 00:21:35,196
Yui!

422
00:21:35,229 --> 00:21:35,696
Yui!

423
00:21:43,196 --> 00:21:43,663
Yui!

424
00:21:46,696 --> 00:21:47,663
-No.

